text: Auntie used to be at chai chee then bedok block 123, now at defu lane, her ban mian is really the bomb. Her chilli is a must-add, it's not spicy but imparts another dimension to her already crazy awesome banmian. Dunno what she did with her youmian but it's silky smooth.
Decided to give this a try as it is newly opened. The spinach you mian is good. Soup is flavorful and goes well with the chilli sauce.
